            <bug_when>2009-12-03 09:37:46 +0100</bug_when>
            <thetext>The inheritance structure of the DateField is currently misleading. 
- ...
  - qx.ui.form.AbstractSelectBox
    - qx.ui.form.ComboBox
      -  qx.ui.form.DateField

This means that the DateField is implemeting two IFrom* interfaces which should not be possible. 

The solution would be to move the common parts of ComboBox and DateField (text selection and placeholder) to a baseclass and both extend this abstract baseball.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
